What you need to know:

In Nairobi, Knut and Kuppet condemned the government for mistreating tutors and poor handling of the return-to-class plans.Knut asked the ministry to release the school calendar while Kuppet said children should be back in class as soon as possible.Kuppet chairman Omboko Milemba said the union is ready to start negotiations on the 2021-2025 CBA with TSC.